            Pregled vježbi
          </a>
          <a href="#vjezba-1" class="toc-link group flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600 hover:text-orange-600 transition-all duration-300 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-orange-50" data-target="vjezba-1">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-400 rounded-full mr-3 transition-all duration-300"></span>
            1. Proizvođači H₂S iz proteina
          </a>
          <a href="#vjezba-2" class="toc-link group flex items-center text-sm text-gray-600 hover:text-orange-600 transition-all duration-300 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-orange-50" data-target="vjezba-2">
